-- Sumitomo Trust to Buy DBS Asset Management for $119 Million, Nikkei Says
-- B y   K a z u y o   S a w a
-- 2010-12-05T21:37:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-05/sumitomo-trust-to-buy-dbs-asset-management-for-119-million-nikkei-says.html
Sumitomo Trust & Banking Co. of Japan
will acquire DBS Asset Management from DBS Bank of Singapore in
exchange for 10 billion yen ($119 million) in shares of Sumitomo
unit Nikko Asset Management Co., the Nikkei newspaper said,
without citing anyone. The transaction will be signed today, the
report said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kazuyo Sawa in Tokyo at 
 ksawa3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
